{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Php|3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","chapter":3,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":1,"text":"In addition, my brothers and sisters, rejoice in the Lord. To write to you again about this is no trouble for me and is a safeguard for you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":2,"text":"Watch out for the dogs, watch out for the evil workers, watch out for those who mutilate the flesh.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":3,"text":"For we are the circumcision, the ones who worship by the Spirit of God, boast in Christ Jesus, and do not put confidence in the flesh —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":4,"text":"although I have reasons for confidence in the flesh. If anyone else thinks he has grounds for confidence in the flesh, I have more:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":5,"text":"circumcised the eighth day; of the nation of Israel, of the tribe of Benjamin, a Hebrew born of Hebrews; regarding the law, a Pharisee;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":6,"text":"regarding zeal, persecuting the church; regarding the righteousness that is in the law, blameless.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":7,"text":"But everything that was a gain to me, I have considered to be a loss because of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":8,"text":"More than that, I also consider everything to be a loss in view of the surpassing value of knowing Christ Jesus my Lord. Because of him I have suffered the loss of all things and consider them as dung, so that I may gain Christ","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":9,"text":"and be found in him, not having a righteousness of my own from the law, but one that is through faith in Christ —the righteousness from God based on faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":10,"text":"My goal is to know him and the power of his resurrection and the fellowship of his sufferings, being conformed to his death,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":11,"text":"assuming that I will somehow reach the resurrection from among the dead.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":12,"text":"Not that I have already reached the goal or am already perfect, but I make every effort to take hold of it because I also have been taken hold of by Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":13,"text":"Brothers and sisters, I do not consider myself to have taken hold of it. But one thing I do: Forgetting what is behind and reaching forward to what is ahead,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":14,"text":"I pursue as my goal the prize promised by God’s heavenly call in Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":15,"text":"Therefore, let all of us who are mature think this way. And if you think differently about anything, God will reveal this also to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":16,"text":"In any case, we should live up to whatever truth we have attained.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":17,"text":"Join in imitating me, brothers and sisters, and pay careful attention to those who live according to the example you have in us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":18,"text":"For I have often told you, and now say again with tears, that many live as enemies of the cross of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":19,"text":"Their end is destruction; their god is their stomach; their glory is in their shame; and they are focused on earthly things.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":20,"text":"Our citizenship is in heaven, and we eagerly wait for a Savior from there, the Lord Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":3,"verse":21,"text":"He will transform the body of our humble condition into the likeness of his glorious body, by the power that enables him to subject everything to himself.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","chapter":3,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,7,12],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Knowing Christ"},{"beforeVerse":12,"text":"Reaching Forward to God’s Goal"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In addition, my brothers and sisters, rejoice "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:12","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 6:10","book":"2Co","chapter":6,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:18","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the Lord. To write to you again about this is no trouble for me and is a safeguard for you."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 12:12","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":12},{"label":"2Co 6:10","book":"2Co","chapter":6,"verse":10},{"label":"Php 1:18","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Watch out for the dogs, watch out for the evil "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:7","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" workers, watch out for those who mutilate the flesh. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 13:7","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we are the circumcision, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:15","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the ones who worship by the Spirit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:4","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 3:16","book":"1Ti","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of God, boast in Christ Jesus, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:7","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:1","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:15","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" and do not put confidence in the flesh — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gl 6:15","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":15},{"label":"Rm 8:4","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":4},{"label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"1Tm 3:16","book":"1Ti","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Rm 16:7","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Php 1:1","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Php 1:15","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":15},{"label":"1Pt 5:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"although I have reasons for confidence in the flesh. If anyone else thinks he has grounds for confidence in the flesh, I have more: "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:3:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"circumcised the eighth day; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:12","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:25","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 21:4","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":4,"lett